headline: Is Target (TGT) Pricing Reflect Its Value After Recent Share Price Rebound
summary: If you are wondering whether Target's share price still reflects what the business is worth, this article will walk through the key valuation clues behind the stock. Target shares last closed at US$111.28, with returns of 4.8% over 7 days, 13.5% over 30 days, 10.7% year to date, but a 13.0% decline over 1 year and a 25.0% decline over 3 years, widening to a 32.8% decline over 5 years. Recent coverage has focused on how the share price performance over different time frames is influencing...
